description.value: A subset of the Snomed-CT clinical terminology (i.e. coding system) intended for use in the UK, previously named SnomedCTUK, that describes the form of the medicinal substance e.g capsules, tablets, liquid. Required if a specific form has been requested by the prescriber. Any code from the SNOMED CT UK CDA Care Setting Type subset with subset original id 421967003.
